Kim-ku3: Lin2 tioh8 chiong Kai-sat e5 mih8 lap8 hou7 Kai-sat, chiong Siong7-te3 e5 mih8 lap8 hou7 Siong7-te3. (Lou7-ka 20:25).
Cheng5 jit8 Nga2-hui7 kap Eng5-chong in pa-pa chhoa7 in 2 hiann-moai7-a2 khi3 Jit8-goat8-tham5 thit-tho5. In che7 chhia seh8 chin tng5 e5 soann-lou7 chiah kau3-ui7. Lou7-tiong Eng5-chong mng7 pa-pa kong2, ¡§Chiah-nih hng7 e5 lou7 si7 sann2 lang5 lai5 cho7 e5.¡¨ Pa-pa kong2 che si7 lan2 kok e5 cheng3-hu2 eng7 chinn5 chhiann3 kang-lang5 cho7-e5. Jit8-goat8-tham5 chin toa7, na2 chhin-chhiunn7 hai2, pa-pa ka7 in kong2, ¡§Chiah e5 chui2 si7 beh cho3 hoat-tian7 e5 lou7-eng7. Hit peng5 u7 chit8 e5 hoat-tian7-sou2, lan2 chhu3-nih e5 tian7-hoe2, thian7-hong, siu-im-ki, ut-tau2 e5 tian7 long2 si7 tui3 chia sang3 chhut-khi3 e5.¡¨ In loh8-khi3 che7 chun5-a2, Nga2-hui7 thiann pa-pa an2-ni kong2 na2 siunn7, tau3-ti2 si7 sann2-lang5 hiah-nih8 ho2-sim cho3 chit e5 hoat-tian7-sou2, un2-tang3 tioh8 khai chin choe7 chinn5, chiu7 mng7 in pa-pa, in pa-pa kong2, ¡§Che si7 kok-ka e5 chinn5 lai5 khi2 e5.¡¨
Chun5-a2 tit8-tit8 chin3-cheng5, au7-bin7 e5 chhu3 na2 se3-keng khi3. In pa-pa koh kong2, ¡§Lan2 tit-tioh8 kok-ka e5 po2-hou7 kap un-hui7 chin choe7, m7-na7 cho7 toa7-lou7, m7-na7 cho7 hoat-tian7-sou2, ia7 u7 khi2 hak8-hau7, ia7 u7 kun-tui7 po2-hou7 lan2 bian2-siu7 goa7-kok e5 chhim-hai7, ia7 u7 keng2-chhat liah8 phainn2 lang5, hou7 ho2-lang5 an-sim koe3-jit8.¡¨ Eng5-chong kong2, ¡§Pa-pa! Kok-ka thai3 u7 hiah-nih8 choe7 chinn5.¡¨ Pa-pa in3 kong2, ¡§Chiu7-si7 choe3 peh-sinn3 e5 lang5 tak8 e5 lap8-soe3, kok-ka chiah u7 chinn5, sou2-i2 lan2 lap8-soe3 ia7 si7 teh hou7 lan2 hiong2-siu7 khah ho2 e5 seng-oah8.
I che7 e5 chun5-a2 sai2 kau3 Jit8-goat8-tham5 e5 tiong-ng, Nga2-hui7 oat8-thau5 si3-khou-lian3-tng2 khoann3, in-ui7 keng2-ti3 chin sui2 hui-siong5 kam2-kek, ka7 in ko-ko kong2, ¡§Ko-ko li2 khoann3! Hiah e5 soann, hiah-e5 chui2-iann2! Sit8-chai7 chin sui2.¡¨ Eng5-chong siunn7 khi2 Seng3-si te7 3 siu2 ¡§Chhiu7-bak8 chhan5-hng5 chui2-choann5, kiong-chhong toa7-hai2 koan5-soann......¡¨ Chiu7 ti7 chhui3-lai7 se3-siann gim5, (chhiann2 kau3-oan5 gim5 te7-it chat ia7 ho2), Nga2-hui7 ia7 toe3 i gim5, gim5 liau2 in pa-pa chhio3-chhio3 ka7 in kong2, ¡§Lin2 long2 chai, chiah e5 soann, chiah e5 thian-jian5 si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 e5, Siong7-te3 m7-na7 chhong3-cho7 chiah e5 ia7 hou7 lan2 oah8-mia7, hou7 ban7-mih8 seng5-tiong2, lan2 chiah u7 thang chiah8, u7 thang chheng7, u7 thang toa3, Siong7-te3 e5 un pi2 kok-ka khah toa7. Lan2 tui3 kok-ka lap8-soe3, ia7 tioh8 koh-khah hoann-hi2 hian3-kim hou7 Siong7-te3.¡¨
Eng5-chong siunn7 kong2, Siong7-te3 ai3 lan2 e5 hian3-kim m7-chai beh cho3 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7? Pa-pa chiah kong2, ¡§Siong7-te3 ai3 lan2 se3-kan lang5 long2 tit-tioh8 kiu3, u7 kio3 chin choe7 lang5 choan-sim thoan5 to7-li2, in3 Seng3-keng, sia2 to7-li2 e5 chheh, khi2 le2-pai3-tng5, iau2 u7 chin choe7 lang5, chiah e5 long2 tioh8 eng7 chin choe7 chinn5, lan2 tioh8 hong7-hian3 thang hou7 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3 cho3 e5 kang u7 chinn5 thang cho3.¡¨ Eng5-chong kap Nga2-hui7 thiann tioh8 an2-ni chiu7 koat-sim chit le2-pai3 beh khiam7 khah che7 chinn5 thang ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 si5 hian3-kim.
Jit8-thau5 e5 kng chio3 lai5, liang5-hong bi5-bi5-a2 chhoe-lai5, in che7 e5 se3-chiah chun5 ban7-ban7-a2 ti7 chui2 teng2 teh sai2, in e5 sim moa2-moa2 e5 kam2-sia7. (T. T. T. sia2)
2 Geh8 8 Jit8
Kim-ku3: I m7 si7 si2-lang5 e5 Siong7-te3, si7 oah8-lang5 e5 Siong7-te3. (Lou7-ka 20:38)
Chha-put-to 100 ni5-cheng5, ti7 Au-lo5-pa e5 chit8-kok O3-tai7-li7-a e5 su7. Ti7 hit e5 kok u7 chit8 e5 hiunn-sia7 kio3-cho3 He-lu-to7-ki-luh.
Hit-si5 tu2-tu2 si7 hit e5 chhut-mia5 e5 Na2-pho-lun5 Tai7-te3 kap O3-tai7-li7-a teh sio-chian3 e5 si5, sou2-i2 Na2-pho-lun5 keng2 chit e5 sio2 hiunn-sia7 ia7 tioh8 chiam3 khi2-lai5 chiah oe7 eng7-tit, sou2-i2 beng7-leng7 chit8 e5 tai7-chiong3 chhoa7 1 ban7 8 chheng mia5 e5 tai7-kun kong lai5 kau3 chit e5 hiunn-sia7.
Hit si5 tu2-tu2 si7 Koh-oah8-cheh e5 chin3-cheng5 me5. Keh-cha2-khi2 chit e5 hiunn-sia7 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 kong2 kin-a2-jit8 si7 Koh-oah8-cheh, sou2-i2 thau3-cha2, chin hoann-hi2 khi2-lai5, seng khoann3 tang-peng5 e5 soann. Ui7-tioh8 hou7 jit8-thau5 e5 kng chio3 tioh8, u7 kim-sih-sih, oe7 sia7 lang5 e5 bak8-chiu e5 mih8 ti7 soann moa2-moa2 si7. In tioh8 chit8-kiann, chim-chiok khoann3, chiu7-si7 Na2-pho-lun5 e5 kun-tui7 i2-keng kong lai5 kau3 hia lah.
Tai7-ke m7-si7 teh Koh-oah8-cheh e5 hoann-hi2 lah, hiunn-sia7 long2 toa7 io5-choah, toa7 io5-tang7, m7-chai an2-choann2 khah ho2. Hiunn-sia7 e5 gau5-lang5 sann-kap chham-siong5 kong2, Lan2 e5 hiunn-sia7 ia7 bo5 bu2-khi3, ia7 bo5 peng, boe7-thang cho3 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 tau5-hang5.
Tai7-ke siunn7 beh koat-teng7 e5 si5, hit tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 bok8-su khia7 khi2-lai5 kong2: ¡§Chu-ui7, kin-a2-jit8 si7 lan2 chit8-ni5 tiong te7-it hoann-hi2 e5 Koh-oah8-cheh. Chit-khoan2 e5 jit8 m7-thang siunn7 chit-khoan2 siong-sim e5 su7. Kin-a2-jit8 si7 Kiu3-chu2 koh-oah8 e5 jit8, lan2 tai7-ke te7-it tai7-seng tioh8 lai5 pai3-tng5 le2-pai3, o-lo2 kam2-sia7 oah8-oah8 e5 Siong7-te3. Sou2-i2 lin2 tioh8 chiau3-siong5 kong3 toa7-cheng, thang long2 lai5 le2-pai3. Oah8 e5 Siong7-te3 beh chhin-chhiunn7 kou2-cha2 po2-hou7 Mou5-se, Tai7-pit8, I2-sai3-a2, tek-khak ia7 beh po2-hou7 lan2.¡¨
Thiann che, u7 chit8-poann3-e5-a2 bo5 sin3-giong2 e5 lang5 thi2-chhio3 i, chong2-si7 choe3-au7 tai7-ke koat-teng7 chiau3 bok8-su sou2 kong2 e5 lai5 cho3. Khong, khong, khong......... hiunn-sia7 e5 lang5 ti7 chit-khoan2 chin gui5-hiam2 e5 si5 e5 Koh-oah8-cheh le2-pai3, sou2-i2 tui3 tang, tui3 sai, tui3 hia tui3 chia, toa7-lang5, gin2-na2 long2 chu7-chip8 lai5 pai3-tng5. Tui3 soann-teng2 khoann3 chit e5 khoan2-sit e5 tai7-chiong3 siunn7-lai5 siunn7-khi3, siunn7 kong2, ¡§Che tek-khak u7 toa7 e5 ke3-oe7, ti7 chit e5 hiunn-sia7 m7-chai u7 bih loa7-che7 e5 peng ia7 bo5 tek-khak; na7 bo5 in thai3 oe7 hiah-nih peng5-an, chiau3 peng5-siong5 teh le2-pai3.¡¨ Sou2-i2 koann2-kin2 hoat beng7-leng7 li7-khui chit e5 hiunn-sia7. Khong, khong, khong. Pai3-tng5 e5 toa7-cheng tan5 liau2 e5 si5, soann-teng2 i2-keng bo5 khoann3-kinn3 chhiunn, kiam3, lang5 e5 iann2.
Sio2-peng5-iu2, lan2 e5 Siong7-te3 si7 oah8 e5 Siong7-te3, lan2 bo5-lun7 pi-siong e5 si5, thang kiann e5 si5, tioh8 oe7 ki3-tit, oah8 e5 Siong7-te3 teh po2-hou7 lan2, chiau3-kou3 lan2, put-si5 kap lan2 sann-kap ti7-teh.
Sann-kap liam7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 kim-ku3. (T. H. C. sia2)
