Kim-ku3: Li2 tioh8 chin7 sim, chin7 seng3, chin7 i3, chin7 lat8 thiann3 Chu2, chiu7-si7 li2 e5 Siong7-te3......koh tioh8 thiann3 li2 e5 chhu3-pinn chhin-chhiunn7 ka-ki7. (Ma2-kho2 12:29,30)
Tng lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou iau2 ti7 se3-kan e5 si5 u7 keng-hak8-su7, kap ka3 lut8-hoat e5 sian-sinn, in chin ai3 chhoe7 phang7 lai5 ki-chhi3, a2-si7 pok8-to2 Ia5-sou. U7 chit8-pai2 in eng7 sim2-mih8 si7 choe3 toa7 e5 kai3 lai5 mng7 Ia5-sou. In e5 i3-su3 si7 ai3 hian2-beng5 in ka-ki7 e5 ho2, ki5-sit8 in e5 sou2-choe3 che7-che7 si7 chin siok8-hoa3, chin ke2-ho2.
Goa2 bat u7 chit8-pai2 thak8 chit8 e5 kou3-su7, kak-tit chin u7 ham5-khng3 ka3-si7, goa2 ti7 chia lai5 kong2 hou7 lin2 thiann. U7 chit8 e5 toa7 seng-li2 lang5, i si7 tiam3 ti7 Hi-liap8 e5 Ko-lim5-to, Ko-lim5-to si7 tong-si5 e5 toa7 kang2-khau2. I peng5-si5 si7 choe3 bou7-ek8-siong, chiu7-si7 tui3 pun2-kok theh8 che7-che7 but8-san2 khi3 goa7-kok, ia7 tui3 goa7-kok chiah be2 che7-che7 goa7-kok-hoe3 to3-lai5 pun2-kok. Put-chi2 hou7-li7, put-chi2 hoat-chai5, ka-ki7 cheng2-chun5, be2 chin che7 lou5-chai5, eng7 in choe3 chui2-siu2 lai5 ko3-chun5. Tong-si5 e5 kau-thong si7 eng7 koa3-phang5 e5 chun5 lai5 koe3-hai2, bo5 hong e5 si5 chiu7 kui2-na7 chap8-lang5 lai5 io5-lou2, ko3-chun5, eng7 an2-ni lai5 kau-thong.
U7 chit8 pai2 i tui3 Ai-kip8 be2 tioh8 boan2-chai3 e5 tiu5-toan7 pou3-phit, i2-kip8 chin che7 e5 toa7-beh8, kap ki5-thann e5 ho2-mih8, beh to3-khi3 in Hi-liap8. Peng5-si5 i kau3-kek8 gek8-thai7 hiah e5 chui2-siu2, siat-su2 u7 bo5 hap8 i e5 i3-su3 e5, siong5-siong5 eng7 kun3, a2-si7 phoe5-pinn ka7 in phah, u7 si5 hou7 i thai5 si2 hiat-loh8 hai2 e5 ia7 u7. Sit8-chai7 khoan2-thai7 hiah e5 lou5-chai5 tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiunn7 khoan2-thai7 gu5, be2 chit8-iunn7, tui3 lang5 ia7-si7 kek8 khek-pok8, pang3 tang7-li7, kau-kiat phainn2-lang5 lai5 lek8-sek lang5.
Tann chit pai2 chun5 kiann5 kau3 poann3 hai2, hut-jian5 tu2-tioh8 hong-thai, kui2-na7 jit8 long2 bo5 khoann3-kinn3 jit8, goeh8, chhinn e5 kng. M7-na7 loh8-phang5, ia7 i2-keng hiat-kak8 chit8-pou7-hun7 khah tang7 e5 mih8, i2-kip8 chit8-pou7-hun7 e5 toa7-beh8. Na7-si7 hong long2 bo5 khah tiam7, toa7 eng2 iu5-goan5 chit8-e7, chit8-e7 phoah koe3 i e5 chun5-pho teng2, put-lun7 i eng7 pinn lai5 phah, eng7 kun3 lai5 kong3 hiah e5 lou5-chai5, sim7-chi3 u7 e5 hou7 i phah-si2, to-si7 sai2 be7 chin3-cheng5. Hit si5 i chiu7 tui3 i e5 sin5-beng5 lu2-sin5, na2-chun2 lan2 Tai5-oan5 se3-siok8 lang5 sou2 sin3 e5 Ma2-chou2-po5 lai5 he7-goan7. I kong2 i na7 e7-tit kiu3 peng5-an kau3 chhu3 u7 mia7 chiu7 ho2, i kam-goan7 chiong chun5 sou2 u7 e5 lai5 hian3, beh koh ka7 lu2-sin5 teng5 khi2 bio7.
Ko2-jian5 u7-iann2 hong chiam7-chiam7 tiam7 khi3, eng2 ia7 penn5 lah. Hit si5 i chin hou7-hoe2, kong2 beh chai ia7 mai3 hian3 hiah che7. Au7-lai5 i chiu7 ka7 lu2-sin5 kong2, goa2 sin3 li2 m7 ai3 te7-chu2 hiah long7-hui3, bio7 to iau2 ho2-ho2, to iau2 e7 toa3 tit, goa2 lai5 ka7 li2 iu5-chhat chiu7 ho2 lah.
Kau3 chhu3 e5 si5 chit8 e5 hoann2 koe3 sann-tang, soa3 kong2 chit-si5 chin put keng2-khi3, goa2 sin3 lu2-sin5 li2 un2-tang3 m7 ai3 lang5 long7-hui3, lo5-sim, sun2-chinn5. Goa2 goan7 hian3 chit8-tui3 gu5-iunn5, ng3-bang7 li2 kam3-lap8, koh bo5 loa7-ku2, bo5 phah-sng3 i e5 seng-li2 u7 sio2-khoa2 liau2-chinn5, i chiu7 chin m7-goan7, soa3 khan-thoa lu2-sin5 bo5 po2-pi3, chiu7 chhu2-siau i e5 gu5-iunn5, chi2-u7 theh8 tam7-poh8 chhin-chhiunn7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 lang5 teh hian3 e5 mi7-ku khi3 hian3 na7-tiann7.
Li2 ka7 i khoann3 chit e5 lang5, peng5-si5 m7-bat teh keng3-sin5, su7 kau3 e5 si5 chiu7 khau3-loa7 i e5 sin5-beng5, su7 koe3-liau2 e5 si5 i chiu7 be7 ki3-tit, ji5-chhiann2 soa3 koe3-siau3 i e5 sin5-beng5 bo5 po2-pi3. Chit-khoan2 sim e5 keng3-sin5 li2 siunn7 tioh8, a2 m7-tioh8. M7-tioh8, chin kian3-siau3, an2-ni i e5 sim si7 liah8 sin5 choe3 i e5 lou5-chai5, si7 kap i siang7-khoan2 pang-chan7 i e5 tham-sim e5 lang5.
Ia5-sou e5 si5-tai7 e5 Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 ia7 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 su-siunn2, ka3 lang5 khek-pok8 pe7-bo2, ia7 chiah lai5 hian3 pok8-ho5, ma2-khun5, kek8 sio2-khoa2 e5 mih8, lai5 beh piau2-si7 i keng3-sin5 e5 jiat8-sim. Sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3, chin chha-biu7 Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7.
Keng3-sin5 m7-si7 an2-ni. Te7-it si7 lai7-sim, lai7-sim u7 chi3-seng5, chin-chiann3 si7 chin7-sim, chin7-seng3, chin7-i3 chin7-lat8 lai5 thiann3 Chu2. Koh tui3 pe7-bo2, hiann-ti7, chhu3-pinn lai5 hian2-beng5 bo5 ke2 e5 thiann3-sim. Che chiah si7 chin-chiann3 e5 keng3-sin5.
Tann cha2-khi2 lan2 tioh8 lai5 hoan2-seng2, lan2 koe3-khi3 e5 keng3-pai3 Sin5, Siong7-te3 si7 eng7 sim2-mih8 khoan2-sit. Lan2 bat eng7 goa7-phoe5, ki5-sit8 lan2 u7 kau3 khian5-seng5 a2-bo5? Lan2 na7 u7-iann2 thiann3 Siong7-te3, ia7 un2-tang3 e7 thiann3 lang5 chiah tioh8, u7 a2-bo5? (L. J. S. sia2)
